{"tid":828454,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「Dancing Queen」Momo 將成為《Dancing High》特別評審","createTime":"2018-09-19T16:37:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-20T04:25:08.000Z","uid":74065,"like":5,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d8964a6732d81ca8c9b1fa1c8af49db404e119cf","tid":828454,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T16:37:54.000Z","msg":"開播後話題不斷的新節目《Dancing High》由鄭亨敦擔任主持人，邀請到著名編舞老師Lia Kim，舞團Just Jerk、李起光、李浩沅、李昇勳擔任導師，華麗的導師名單也讓人對節目更加期待啊！<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.wishnote.tw/550/2018/09/19/550_1312687_1537339313.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2018%2F09%2F19%2F550_1312687_1537339313.webp&h=0b14e419&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最新一集公開的預告中，讓人眼睛一亮的是「TWICE的Momo」和「請夏」，兩位女神驚喜現身！將擔任特別評審的她們也引起大家的好奇啊！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n節目組更透露，有「Dancing Queen」之稱的Momo展現了驚人的分析能力，也為這些年紀只有10幾歲的舞者加油打氣。請夏看完這些舞者們的對決舞台後更表示「我好像變成粉絲了，舞蹈非常帥氣！」<br />\n<br />\n請夏在I.O.I時期舞蹈實力就相當厲害，先前還有參加過《Hit The Stage》，甚至邀請有請一起表演。在《Hit The Stage》中展現了充滿力量的舞蹈，以及請夏自己獨特的魅力。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86bfb04c0eed52ae2f709a1d9bfa985e2b3145ac","tid":828454,"uid":42212,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T16:39:00.000Z","msg":"支持我老婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbdca4187aca0901676091bbfbecb6f10013ce73","tid":828454,"uid":63057,"like":7,"dislike":5,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T01:00:58.000Z","msg":"實至名歸<br />\nmomo 跳舞實力四代女團第一"},{"pid":"42dcc02e128505e2702ccf22da428e11c1e2eb40","tid":828454,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"bbdca4187aca0901676091bbfbecb6f10013ce73","tid":828454,"uid":63057,"like":7,"dislike":5,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T01:00:58.000Z","msg":"實至名歸<br />\nmomo 跳舞實力四代女團第一"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T04:25:08.000Z","msg":"由百名愛豆選出跳舞最強<br />\n實至名歸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}